{
  "name": "RPlog_Argon_s_Awards",
  "title": "Argon's Awards",
  "summary": "On the New Republic parade grounds, a grand military awards ceremony honors those whose service secured the liberation of Bothawui. Chief of State Leia Organa Solo presides from the podium, opening with a solemn tribute to the Bothan sacrifice and the long road still ahead before their homeworld is free. Among the seated honorees is the nervous Corellian Lt. Commander Argon Brand, commanding officer of the Lightbringer, who is called forward for special commendation. Leia personally upgrades his epaulet and offers a warm, reassuring whisper about the fine fare awaiting at the reception. As the recipients bask in the crowd's applause and the swelling music, Argon's anxiety melts into quiet pride. The ceremony closes smoothly, and Argon rejoins his parents for the refreshments while Leia is whisked away to her next duty.",
